This paper discusses the use of Recurrent Neural Networks in various natural language processing and computer vision tasks, which are typically covered in the arXiv sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Systems and Control (cs.SD), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
